OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FPaul is one of around twenty thousand
OL,8,Funpaid carers estimated to be living
OL,9,Fin Dumfries and Galloway by the
OL,10,Fregions carers centre. Staff believe
OL,11,Fthere could be more; people who look
OL,12,Fafter elderly or sick relatives
OL,13,Fwithout quite seeing themselves as
OL,14,Fcarers.
OL,16,F'You'll reach a breaking point'
OL,18,FYoung carers are also vulnerable to
OL,19,Fisolation, with some having to give up
OL,20,Fsocial time with friends in order to
OL,21,Fcare for relatives.
