OL,3,C'It's 15 months since he left that
OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThirteen-year-old Rachael said "my
OL,8,Ffriends like going out...obviously I
OL,9,Fcan't do that most of the time because
OL,10,FI have to help it after my sister."
OL,12,FHowever, she was keen to stress the
OL,13,Fbenefits of caring, as she enjoys a
OL,14,Fclose relationship with her younger
OL,15,Fsister.
OL,17,F"We've got a really good
OL,18,Frelationship," she said.
