OL,3,C'It's 15 months since he left that
OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"Although someone has a disability,
OL,8,Fthey're just like the same as everyone
OL,9,Felse. And just because they have a
OL,10,Fdisability, it doesn't mean that they
OL,11,Fcan't do things."
OL,13,FThe role unpaid carers perform is
OL,14,Fvital, not just to their loved ones,
OL,15,Fbut to the wider health service. A
OL,16,Fnumber of hospitals in the region,
OL,17,Fincluding and the , have put out
OL,18,Fstatements in 2024 suggesting that
OL,19,Fservices threaten to be overwhelmed.
