OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThis can be down to an inability to
OL,8,Fdischarge patients from hospital, even
OL,9,Fif they're well enough to go home, due
OL,10,Fto a lack of suitable care options in
OL,11,Fthe community.
OL,13,FPaul told ITV News that, without him,
OL,14,Fhis Dad could have been in hospital
OL,15,Ffor "months" while health officials
OL,16,Ftried to build a care package for him.
OL,18,F'Something drastic is needed'
