OL,3,C'It's 15 months since he left that
OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe carers centre Chief Office
OL,8,FClaudine Brindle said a National Care
OL,9,FService in could be the way to improve
OL,10,Fthe situation, given the regions
OL,11,Fageing population.
OL,13,FA bill to create one in Scotland is
OL,14,Fcurrently being reviewed in Holyrood.
OL,15,FIf passed, the Scottish Government
OL,16,Fwant to transfer responsibility for
OL,17,Fsocial care to a new, nationwide
OL,18,Fservice.
