OL,3,C'It's 15 months since he left that
OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"If all those things can be introduced
OL,8,Fright across Scotland, that's
OL,9,Fsomething that hopefully would make a
OL,10,Fdifference. And obviously that's a
OL,11,Fjourney that we're at the beginning of
OL,12,Fat the moment."
OL,14,FPaul now receives help, with a paid
OL,15,Fcarer coming round most mornings to
OL,16,Fhelp wash and dress his Dad. But he
OL,17,Fsays the support is "barely" there,
OL,18,Fsuggesting that more needs to be done.
