OL,7,F"I know the people that care for my
OL,8,Fdad are short staffed and the rotation
OL,9,Fof people is very limited," he said.
OL,11,FA National Care Service for Scotland?
OL,13,FThe Scottish Government has said it's
OL,14,Fcommitted to establishing a nationwide
OL,15,Fcare service across Scotland.
