OL,4,Croom:' Unpaid carers call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThey said the service, which they want
OL,8,Fto introduce by 2028, would
OL,9,Fstandardise care across the country
OL,10,Fand support unpaid carers. Currently,
OL,11,Fmost social care is provided by local
OL,12,Fauthorities.
OL,14,FIn a statement the Health and Social
OL,15,FCare Partnership said: "Without the
OL,16,Fvital role played by the thousands of
OL,17,Funpaid Carers in our region, our
OL,18,Fhealth and social care systems simply
OL,19,Fcould not function.
